name: Army Humvee 3D Parking Simulator - Realistic Car Driving Test
name_original: Army Humvee 3D Parking Simulator - Realistic Car Driving Test
description:
Start your engines!! In this fun realistic driving test game, you get to drive an Army Humvee! Start, stop, back up, and work your way around this army base as you try to test your skills through various parking challenges.

FEATURES

- Realistic 3D Army base.
- Easy controls.
- Multi direction camera controls.
